  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Add your <strong>white long grain rice</strong> to a pot with a lid with 225ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [300ml]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[450ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked then remove from the heat and set aside (lid on) to steam until serving</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
