            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> into thin slices (2 per person!) and squeeze the juice of the <strong>remaining lemon </strong>into a bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>honey</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> of your <strong>cornflour</strong>,<strong> half</strong> your <strong>soy sauce </strong>(save the rest for later!) and 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>to the bowl</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>lemon sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1708332548163-x200.jpg",
