    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Cut your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Stir the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong> and <strong>chopped chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) into the cooked rice – this is your<strong> chilli rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
