        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>crispy hake </strong>with the <strong>chilli rice </strong>and<strong> roasted Tenderstem broccoli </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>lemon sauce</strong> over the hake and garnish with the <strong>lemon slices</strong> and your<strong> toasted sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
